Text.string: Here's how you make an entrance!
Viewers, comment on the stream and tell us how you want the Vault Thief to die! We've got moderators standing by.
Hey! “Knife” to meet you! Haha, get it?
You can't cut it, but we can!
By popular demand... it's the mega-blender!
Let's cut you down to size!
Time to tender you up... with the Tenderizer!
We're gonna need a mop for you.
Aren't ya a little tall for a Vault Thief? Let's fix that.
Our Vault Thief is on fire! (laughing) Or -- or at least, they're about to be.
This isn't over! Terror! Hit them directly with the Eridium Core! Oh, what's that? Unstable? I don't care, just do it!
The Vault Thief's puttin' up a hell of a fight. Terror, you can press those buttons faster, right?
Okay, break's over. We're all in! Terror! Hit every button!
Hell's bells, Terror! This thing's comin' apart!

Time for a quick commercial break! Our ammunition sponsor today is Marcus Munitions! I got some, uh, copy to read here... “Cult wackos, get stuffed”? Hey, pal -- I'll take your money, but that's just unprofessional.
Make some noise, you filthy animals!
Whoa-whoa-whoa, NO! This is all wrong! We're the star of the show! Not YOU!
Woah! Hey, Terror! This thing could use some padding inside.
NOOOOOOOO! Agh, put the -- fff -- ouch!
Oh, for the love of the Twins!
You've GOT to be kidding me!
What kinda show do you think this is?
All eyes on you, Vault Thief!
Terror, show them what they've won!
Hah! You're not cut out for the big time, Vault Thief!
Not much of a show, folks. Next time we'll get someone a little more vicious, like a... sedated rabbit or a pet rock!
What are you doin'? These people aren't paying to watch nap time! That's a totally different show!
Guess they're done for! Release the skags!
Ahh, let the skags finish 'em off.
Now for the audience participation segment. Get in there and show the Vault Thief how sharp your teeth are!
Now accepting all contenders to the stage!
Come on down and join the fight! No waivers needed!
Here's a fan favorite: a big giant knife!
